videos.headline: Caps watch party erupts when they win the Cup
videos.description: Capital One Arena goes wild when the clock runs out and Washington secures its first-ever Stanley Cup.

videos.headline: Ovechkin did it all en route to Conn Smythe
videos.description: Steve Levy and Barry Melrose praise Alex Ovechkin's postseason, saying he contributed even when he wasn't scoring goals.
